TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_PAYOR_AGT, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_PAYOR_AGY, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_PAYEE_AGT, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_PAYEE_AGY, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_RECRUIT_TYPE, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_UPDATE_BY, IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.DTE_UPDATE, TO_DATE(L.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') DTE_CYCLE, SYSDATE DTE_EXTRACT, 1 DEC_STATUS FROM IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP, IN_ETL_CONTROL L WHERE L.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_NADOR_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP.TXT_GROUP IN (SELECT MAX(TXT_GROUP) FROM IN_NADOR_PAYEE_SETUP_TEMP)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE in_etl_control S SET s.txt_key_value = (SELECT TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_NADOR_CYCLE_DATE'), s.dte_update_date = sysdate WHERE s.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_NADOR_MAX_CYCLE_DATE' AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_NADOR_CYCLE_DATE' AND NVL(DEC_ENFORCE_FLG,0)=1 );
COMMIT;
